data.description: Welcome home to 103 Chandler St. perfectly situated in the highly sought after neighborhood of Forest Hills. This charming 3 bedroom 2 full bath home has been thoughtfully and meticulously maintained and improved. Upon arriving take note of the well manicured landscaping complete with fresh pine straw in the flower beds that give this corner lot the perfect curb appeal. Enter through the freshly painted front door where you will be greeted by lovely hardwood floors that run throughout this home. The floorpan flows comfortably and conveniently. The warm inviting living room features a gorgeous gas log fireplace that has been recently updated with a German Schmear treatment that will have all your guest raving!This amazing fireplace also divides the living and dining rooms giving you an amazing accent wall that creates the perfect ambiance to enjoy while eating all your meals. The kitchen is very spacious and offers ample counter and cabinet space ideal for any level of chef. On the other end of this incredible turn key home is where you will find the primary bedroom and full bath room. Here you will enjoy your large bedroom with dual closets, one of which is a walk in. There is a nook perfect for a vanity and the bathroom features a lovely tile shower. There is even a separate entrance to the back deck with the perfect spot to enjoy your morning coffee. Off the hallway you will also find the second and third bedroom both nicely sized and the guest bathroom which has also been freshly painted and updated with new hardware, mirror, and fixtures. This home truly has it all even a bonus room off of the kitchen perfect for a den or game room. The laundry rooms is very large and is great for added storage. When you step out onto the back porch make sure to look up and take note of the beautiful wood ceilings. The back deck has also been freshly painted and is an awesome spot for summer bbqs and back yard parties! You do not want to miss the chance to own this one of a kind gem located walking distance to parks, tennis courts, the Great Swamp Sanctuary, Downtown Walterboro, and so much more. Not to mention you are minutes from I-95, Charleston, Beaufort, and Savannah. Every detail has been thought through for you from the outside landscaping to the hardware and fixtures inside and everything in between all you need to do is move in! Call today to schedule your showing!
